quests.desc: Get ready to pick stuff up and put it in places, because you've just entered TextWorld! First, it would be fantastic if you could move west. Following that, go west. Following that, make an attempt to head south. And then, attempt to venture south. That done, try to head east. And then, make an attempt to take a trip east. Okay, and then, move north. And then, attempt to travel west. Then, take the banana from the case in the kitchenette. And then, toss the banana on the floor of the kitchenette. That's it!

objective: Welcome to TextWorld! First, it would be a great idea if you could attempt to travel west. And then, travel west. That done, go to the south. With that over with, head south. That done, attempt to venture east. With that accomplished, make an effort to head east. With that done, try to go to the north. And then, go to the west. Okay, and then, retrieve the banana from the case within the kitchenette. After taking the banana, deposit the banana on the floor of the kitchenette. Alright, thanks!

main_quest.desc: Welcome to TextWorld! First, it would be a great idea if you could attempt to travel west. And then, travel west. That done, go to the south. With that over with, head south. That done, attempt to venture east. With that accomplished, make an effort to head east. With that done, try to go to the north. And then, go to the west. Okay, and then, retrieve the banana from the case within the kitchenette. After taking the banana, deposit the banana on the floor of the kitchenette. Alright, thanks!
